  "detailed_description": "<strong>- The Sand Dunes -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.poster.avif?t=1636587318\" width=608 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.webm?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.mp4?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The Sand Dunes is an action game with shooter and bullet hell elements. You will have to complete levels exploring and defeating multiple enemies.<br><br>Delve into <i>Diana</i>'s last mission.<br>Liberate your brother <i>Amit</i> and the other Gods from their destruction and vengeance desires.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong><i>Explore</i> the dunes. Find secrets and upgrades (new spells, or stats boosts).</strong><br><br></li><li> <strong><i>Complete</i> different challenges in order to unlock secret zones or to continue the adventure.</strong><br><br></li><li> <strong><i>Defeat</i> multiple bosses and survive chaotic battles using your spells, dashes and magic shields.</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.poster.avif?t=1636587318\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.webm?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.mp4?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>- The Sand Dunes -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.poster.avif?t=1636587318\" width=608 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.webm?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/075e4713a7828199cbd3ea17d869e387.mp4?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The Sand Dunes is an action game with shooter and bullet hell elements. You will have to complete levels exploring and defeating multiple enemies.<br><br>Delve into <i>Diana</i>'s last mission.<br>Liberate your brother <i>Amit</i> and the other Gods from their destruction and vengeance desires.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong><i>Explore</i> the dunes. Find secrets and upgrades (new spells, or stats boosts).</strong><br><br></li><li> <strong><i>Complete</i> different challenges in order to unlock secret zones or to continue the adventure.</strong><br><br></li><li> <strong><i>Defeat</i> multiple bosses and survive chaotic battles using your spells, dashes and magic shields.</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.poster.avif?t=1636587318\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.webm?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566610/extras/a350f120c2b77a5555ac9a85ad81352c.mp4?t=1636587318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vide